data.meta_description: Friday Night Dead: With Albert Sahley. "Friday Night Dead" was a hosted horror movie show with Al Sahley as "Fat Drac" presenting movies on Friday nights on WVAH-TV, Fox Channel 11 Charleston-Huntington, West Virginia in the early 1980s.
